1. /movies/ --> GET

[
	{
		title: str
		description: str
		release_date: date/str
		num_of_actors: int
		(num_of_votes: int)
	},
	{
		title: str
		description: str
		release_date: date/str
		num_of_actors: int
		(num_of_votes: int)
	},

	...

	{
		title: str
		description: str
		release_date: date/str
		num_of_actors: int
		(num_of_votes: int)
	}

]

2. /actors/  --> GET

[
	{
		name: str
		dob: date/str
		num_of_movies: int
	},
	{
		name: str
		dob: date/str
		num_of_movies: int
	},

	...
	
	{
		name: str
		dob: date/str
		num_of_movies: int
	}
]

3. 
	GET

   /movies/?ordering=title
   /movies/?ordering=release_date
   /movies/?ordering=title,release_date

   https://www.django-rest-framework.org/api-guide/filtering/#orderingfilter

4. POST
   
   /movies/<id>/vote or /movies/vote/<id> or some other endpoint

   {
   		vote: "upvote/downvote"
   }

   or
   {
   		vote : 1 / -1
   }


